Hey guys I decided to try out Warwick in the jungle today after a long time and it got me wondering on some different builds that might work on him. Currently most people run AD Tank/Attack speed but I also thought maybe going hybrid could also work since his AP scaling on his Q is 1:1 making it quite powerful in damage and healing tons if building AP. So here are some builds I have thought of might work:

