The first one is my standard build I would go for giving a good mix of AD and AP with the added heal from Gunblade and the bonus damage from Nashors, plus Guinsoos OP.
The second build is if your looking for a bit more AD with some extra life steal.
The third build gives you a bit of extra health with the added movement speed and armour reduction from Black Cleaver. Also which boots you build I would get according to your matchups but it&#039;s up to you.

I would appreciate your feedback and ideas of anything better I could add to these builds!
